<div id="review_1764477430" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1764477430" />
    <a title="Sooz" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7575584-sooz"><img alt="Sooz" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1358439532p2/7575584.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1764477430?book_show_action=true">Sep 29, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sooz" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sooz" href="/user/show/7575584-sooz">Sooz</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7575584-sooz?shelf=powerful-impactful">powerful-impactful</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7575584-sooz?shelf=great-storytelling">great-storytelling</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7575584-sooz?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7575584-sooz?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7575584-sooz?shelf=permanent-shelf">permanent-shelf</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7575584-sooz?shelf=relationship-stories">relationship-stories</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1764477430" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10248271858326627862">This story moved me incredibly, although there were times that it tore at my heart. The main character, Asahel Linden, was The Sojourner, traveling through life immersed in his heart and in his philosophical thoughts. Some of this, I identified with, but when the cruel actions of those close to him had impact, I thought to myself, &quot;I would have fought back with actions just as heartless.&quot; Asahel was incapable of fighting, although he stood his ground firmly. I felt angry, sometimes not sure that</span>
  <span id="freeText10248271858326627862" style="display:none">This story moved me incredibly, although there were times that it tore at my heart. The main character, Asahel Linden, was The Sojourner, traveling through life immersed in his heart and in his philosophical thoughts. Some of this, I identified with, but when the cruel actions of those close to him had impact, I thought to myself, "I would have fought back with actions just as heartless." Asahel was incapable of fighting, although he stood his ground firmly. I felt angry, sometimes not sure that I wanted to continue reading, so frustrated was I with someone whose values were close to my own. A moving tale, indeed, it will go on my permanent shelf. How grateful I am that I came across it on a thrift store shelf, because it is out of print and I would never have even known about it. </span>
  <a data-text-id="10248271858326627862" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


