        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3606618016" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5061185029615639059">I read this book as a high school senior in 1955 and didn&apos;t understand it. I just finished it again and fully agree with most other reviewers. We have to realize that life in those times was as simple as we&apos;d like it to be and as complex as it is now. <br/>Technically, Rawlings&apos; character and setting development is as good as I&apos;ve read in any other work. <br/>If you are looking for rapid action and unpredictable twists in the plot - don&apos;t bother. But if you are looking for a realistic story of those times</span>
  <span id="freeText5061185029615639059" style="display:none">I read this book as a high school senior in 1955 and didn't understand it. I just finished it again and fully agree with most other reviewers. We have to realize that life in those times was as simple as we'd like it to be and as complex as it is now. <br />Technically, Rawlings' character and setting development is as good as I've read in any other work. <br />If you are looking for rapid action and unpredictable twists in the plot - don't bother. But if you are looking for a realistic story of those times - spend some rainy afternoons with it.</span>
  <a data-text-id="5061185029615639059" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


